tees executive profile christa s quarles cfachief executive officer of opentable inc the priceline group incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background ms christa s quarles cfa has been the chief executive officer of opentable inc at the priceline group inc since november   ms quarles served as an interim chief executive officer and chief financial officer of opentable inc until november   she leads the global business strategy and vision for opentable she served as the chief business officer for nextdoorcom inc where she oversaw finance business intelligence hr business development  and legal she served as the chief financial officer of playdom inc since december  and served as its vice president she joined playdom in december  she served as the senior vice president and general manager at disney where she led the mobile and social games divisions within the walt disney company she joined disney in  as part of the acquisition of playdom where she served as chief financial officer in her career she spent ten years as an equity research analyst covering the internet sector at thomas weisel partners now stifel financial and served as its managing director in the equity research group she served as managing director and senior equity research analyst of thomas weisel partners equity research she covered the internet sector at the thomas weisel partners since  as the lead internet analyst she was responsible for developing the thomas weisel partnerss research themes and conducts proprietary research on the dynamics of the secular shifts of interactive advertising and media consumption she served as managing director of thomas weisel partners group prior to thomas weisel she served as a summer associate at morgan stanley investment management analyzing media stocks prior to that she served as an assistant vice president and equity analyst at bofa merrill lynch research division where she worked in the fixedincome research department analyzing bond portfolios for institutional accounts she has been an independent director of kimberlyclark corporation since june   she was recognized by greenwich associates forbes and starmine for her work in the space she holds a cfa designation ms quarles graduated with a bs in economics and german from carnegie mellon university where she graduated first in the department of economics received university and college honors and was named to phi beta kappa she also holds an mba from the harvard business schoolread full background corporate headquarters  connecticut avenuenorwalk connecticut united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentindependent directorkimberlyclark corporation education mba harvard business schoolbs carnegie mellon university other affiliations opentable inckimberlyclark corporationharvard business schoolcarnegie mellon universitybofa merrill lynch research divisionthomas weisel partners equity researchplaydom incnextdoorcom inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepositioncompanycompensationdevin n wenig chief executive officer president and directorebay incmrichard d fain chairman and chief executive officerroyal caribbean cruises ltdmmichael oleary ceo  executive directorryanair holdings plcmyanhong li cofounder chairman and chief executive officerbaidu incdara khosrowshahi chief executive officer president director